                <div1>
                <pb n="0153a" id="I01.0060.0153a" ed="I"/>
                <lb ed="I" n="0153a00"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 60</head>
                <lb ed="I" n="0153a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>趙郡王高叡定國寺碑</title></jhead></juan>
                <lb ed="I" n="0153a00"/><mulu level="1" label="碑陽" type="其他"/><head>碑陽</head>
                    <div2>
                    <lb ed="I" n="0153a00"/><mulu level="2" label="額" type="其他"/><head>額</head>
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153a01"/>大齊
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153a02"/>趙郡
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153a03"/>王□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153a04"/>□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153a05"/>之碑
                    </div2>
                    <div2>
                    <lb ed="I" n="0153b00"/><mulu level="2" label="本文" type="其他"/><head>本文</head>
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b01"/><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">蓋</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">聞</unclear>珠林琁室。現崑崙之中。銀闕金宮。跱蓬萊之上。居之□<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">幽</unclear>。登之乃靈。逐雨隨風。懸殊六通之<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">果</unclear>。黃衣丹椹。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">亦</unclear>非四<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">類</unclear>之味。況□陽止□之洞。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">省</unclear>□□大帝之□。□□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b02"/>生半天之山。七盧入香煙之岳。伏膺道術。始學牛毛。於我法門。事均驢乳。次復月光童子。戲天台之傍。仁祠浮圖。繞嵩高之側。行藏比於幻化。出沒放於淨土。弗□□□。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b03"/>罕逢濡足。及於金臺羅漢。遠住東海。瓊樹聲聞。遙家西域。承風問道。此實闕如。豈若太玄<note n="0153001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30479;＝所【中研院】</note><app n="0153001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30479;</rdg></app>都。化作<note n="0153002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30884;＝經【中研院】</note><app n="0153002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">經</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30884;</rdg></app>行之境。真人<note n="0153003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30479;＝所【中研院】</note><app n="0153003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30479;</rdg></app>府。翻成息心之地。黃河之北。忽出育王之龕。<note n="0153004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01470;＝蔥【中研院】</note><app n="0153004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">蔥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01470;</rdg></app>□
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b04"/>之<note n="0153005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">柬＝東【中研院】</note><app n="0153005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">東</lem><rdg wit="【原】">柬</rdg></app>。別有迦維之國。然燈避風之<note n="0153006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30529;＝處【中研院】</note><app n="0153006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">處</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30529;</rdg></app>。服藥息務之<note n="0153007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30479;＝所【中研院】</note><app n="0153007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30479;</rdg></app>。和合戾止。有朱山焉。其地則上應琁星。下分<note n="0153008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30928;＝全【中研院】</note><app n="0153008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">全</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30928;</rdg></app>趙。邑&CB00528;靈丘。念黑貂之為珥。峰連牛飲。吐白陸之滋川。重嶺<note n="0153009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30885;＝概【中研院】</note><app n="0153009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">概</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30885;</rdg></app>雲。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">苙</unclear>
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b05"/>人或凡。曲<note n="0153010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00117;＝澗【中研院】</note><app n="0153010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">澗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00117;</rdg></app>無<note n="0153011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30886;＝底【中研院】</note><app n="0153011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">底</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30886;</rdg></app>。瞻天謂<note n="0153012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00275;＝窗【中研院】</note><app n="0153012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">窗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00275;</rdg></app>。晨光東壑。類湯谷密<note n="0153013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30887;＝邇【中研院】</note><app n="0153013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">邇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30887;</rdg></app>。暮色西巘。<note n="0153014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30888;＝怪【中研院】</note><app n="0153014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">怪</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30888;</rdg></app>崦嵫咫尺。<note n="0153015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30291;＝陰【中研院】</note><app n="0153015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">陰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30291;</rdg></app>冰夏素。想逼燭龍。陽木冬青。意近火<note n="0153016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30889;＝鼠【中研院】</note><app n="0153016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">鼠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30889;</rdg></app>。重巖之面有<note n="0153017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30890;＝瀑【中研院】</note><app n="0153017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">瀑</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30890;</rdg></app>布焉。至於春泉初涌。秋水時至。蕭
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b06"/><note n="0153018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB05007;＝條【中研院】</note><app n="0153018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">條</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB05007;</rdg></app>圓注。擬虹氛而上昇。散亂高流。狀天河之懸瀉。若乃金花瓊實。&CB00153;日香風。玉酒石膏。除飢卻老。羊腸九&CB00095;。<note n="0153019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00309;＝蛇【中研院】</note><app n="0153019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">蛇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00309;</rdg></app>盤九曲。驅龍從<note n="0153020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02462;＝虎【中研院】</note><app n="0153020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">虎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02462;</rdg></app>。一見而不歸。控鵠<note n="0153021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB18794;＝乘【中研院】</note><app n="0153021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">乘</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB18794;</rdg></app>鸞。蹔遊而忘返。定
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b07"/>州定國寺。禪師僧標身重<note n="0153022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB21061;＝戒【中研院】</note><app n="0153022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">戒</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB21061;</rdg></app>珠。心倫堅石。時和人俗。不染世塵。以其山<note n="0153023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30529;＝處【中研院】</note><app n="0153023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">處</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30529;</rdg></app>閑虛。林幽爽曠。香珍&CB00048;住地之德。清靜賞仁人之心。乃施淨財。云為禪室。於茲廿有餘年矣。背
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b08"/>兔頭之嶺。構柏堂之谷。別房覓崎<note n="0153024" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB04509;＝嶇【中研院】</note><app n="0153024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">嶇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB04509;</rdg></app>之岫。離館逐<note n="0153025" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30891;＝低【中研院】</note><app n="0153025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">低</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30891;</rdg></app>昂之嶮。交藤代幄。懸葛當帷。<note n="0153026" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30892;＝鑿【中研院】</note><app n="0153026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">鑿</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30892;</rdg></app>石開塗。披榛置<note n="0153027" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30893;＝徑【中研院】</note><app n="0153027"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">徑</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30893;</rdg></app>。因山結宇。無勞一匱之勤。即水縈池。非求百姓之力。霧集懃定之
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b09"/>侶。雲歸無漏之人。<note n="0153028" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30401;＝正【中研院】</note><app n="0153028"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">正</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30401;</rdg></app>念不虧。息心相<note n="0153029" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB07622;＝繼【中研院】</note><app n="0153029"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">繼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB07622;</rdg></app>。頭堪孕鳥。心成竹<note n="0153030" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00309;＝蛇【中研院】</note><app n="0153030"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">蛇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00309;</rdg></app>。採椽茅屋。<note n="0153031" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30894;＝藜【中研院】</note><app n="0153031"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">藜</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30894;</rdg></app>羹粟飯。七益不受。三淨不食。是真<note n="0153032" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30895;＝苦【中研院】</note><app n="0153032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">苦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30895;</rdg></app>行。是實頭陀。鐘韻應霜。梵聲傳谷。<note n="0153033" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02462;＝虎【中研院】</note><app n="0153033"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">虎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02462;</rdg></app>音纔振。風神散<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">非</unclear>時
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b10"/>之花。魚鱗已舉。雨伯造清涼之氣。百鳥競鳴。學黑蜂之唱無我。萬籟爭響。寫天樂之娛法王。聞和雅音。咸無生忍。屬　　大齊之馭九有。累聖重<note n="0153034" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30896;＝規【中研院】</note><app n="0153034"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">規</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30896;</rdg></app>。羲軒之流。炎昊之<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">輩</unclear>。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b11"/>出東震。握北<note n="0153035" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30897;＝斗【中研院】</note><app n="0153035"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">斗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30897;</rdg></app>。擊玉<note n="0153036" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30898;＝鼓【中研院】</note><app n="0153036"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">鼓</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30898;</rdg></app>。轉金輪。前疑後承。左賢右<note n="0153037" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30899;＝戚【中研院】</note><app n="0153037"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">戚</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30899;</rdg></app>。數當於天運。名上於河<note n="0153038" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB17573;＝圖【中研院】</note><app n="0153038"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB17573;</rdg></app>。入作股<note n="0153039" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01263;＝肱【中研院】</note><app n="0153039"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">肱</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01263;</rdg></app>。出為蕃屏。使持節都<note n="0153040" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30484;＝督【中研院】</note><app n="0153040"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">督</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30484;</rdg></app>定幽安平東燕滄瀛諸軍事撫軍將軍儀同三司定州
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b12"/><note n="0153041" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30914;＝刺【中研院】</note><app n="0153041"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">刺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30914;</rdg></app>史六州大都<note n="0153042" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30484;＝督【中研院】</note><app n="0153042"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">督</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30484;</rdg></app>趙郡<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">王</unclear>高叡。枝流姜水。氣別大風。昔殷周以稷契立功。虞漢藉軒唐之德。<note n="0153043" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB11040;＝復【中研院】</note><app n="0153043"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB11040;</rdg></app>有<note n="0153044" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01628;＝摠【中研院】</note><app n="0153044"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">摠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01628;</rdg></app>農皇之緒。兼尚父之勳。光奄宇宙。義高前篆。祖同王季。彰積德之<note n="0153045" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">苻＝符【中研院】</note><app n="0153045"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">符</lem><rdg wit="【原】">苻</rdg></app>。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b13"/><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">考</unclear>即劉文。協內謀之議。<note n="0153046" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30926;＝休【中研院】</note><app n="0153046"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">休</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30926;</rdg></app>徵遠降。爰誕異人。封自東門。土分北社。多能將聖。上稟天知。<note n="0153047" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30900;＝幼【中研院】</note><app n="0153047"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">幼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30900;</rdg></app><note n="0153048" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30901;＝秉【中研院】</note><app n="0153048"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">秉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30901;</rdg></app><note n="0153049" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00309;＝蛇【中研院】</note><app n="0153049"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">蛇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00309;</rdg></app>珠。雀臺擒□。□成麟角。<note n="0153050" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02462;＝虎【中研院】</note><app n="0153050"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">虎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02462;</rdg></app>殿論儒。辯樂三雍。富河澗之典。<note n="0153051" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30902;＝驂【中研院】</note><app n="0153051"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">驂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30902;</rdg></app>駕四馬。高柏
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b14"/><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">樑</unclear>之勾。吐握思賢。安勞郭隗之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">策</unclear>。水鏡知士。何有鄒陽之書。故令司馬願遊&CB30883;解。武騎<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">邯</unclear>鄲對見。雅伏天人。忠以奉公。惠以施□。□神敬鬼。織天成地。心將冥會。非<note n="0153052" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB11040;＝復【中研院】</note><app n="0153052"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB11040;</rdg></app>爻
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b15"/><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">象</unclear>攸知。&CB00528;出人表。亦豈名言<note n="0153053" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30479;＝所【中研院】</note><app n="0153053"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30479;</rdg></app>測。劉蒼德茂。彌事謙下。馬孚尊寵。不以為榮。至夫睎面R高。虞巡北岳。中山<note n="0153054" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30903;＝舊【中研院】</note><app n="0153054"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">舊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30903;</rdg></app>國。漢<note n="0153055" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30904;＝號【中研院】</note><app n="0153055"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">號</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30904;</rdg></app>東蕃。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">帝</unclear>摯唐侯。昔封此邑。魏文太子。<note n="0153056" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB11040;＝復【中研院】</note><app n="0153056"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB11040;</rdg></app>鎮斯城。五
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b16"/><note n="0153057" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30905;＝陘【中研院】</note><app n="0153057"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">陘</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30905;</rdg></app>傍通。四關斜<note n="0153058" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31158;＝指【中研院】</note><app n="0153058"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">指</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31158;</rdg></app>。荊卿易水。含燕寒而北流。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">王</unclear>霸呼<note n="0153059" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB05811;＝沱【中研院】</note><app n="0153059"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">沱</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB05811;</rdg></app>。浮漢冰而南<note n="0153060" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00160;＝脈【中研院】</note><app n="0153060"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">脈</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00160;</rdg></app>。地中天府。聞蘇子之言。境<note n="0153061" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB06281;＝寔【中研院】</note><app n="0153061"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">寔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB06281;</rdg></app>神州。具盧□<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">之</unclear>說。海城七十。僅譬閭井。雲夢八九。寧方藪澤。連<note n="0153062" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30906;＝甍【中研院】</note><app n="0153062"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">甍</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30906;</rdg></app>接
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b17"/>棟。煦氣成虹。袨服靚莊。揮汗如雨。先公佐<note n="0153063" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30762;＝世【中研院】</note><app n="0153063"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">世</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30762;</rdg></app>。<note n="0153064" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00573;＝嘗【中研院】</note><app n="0153064"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">嘗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00573;</rdg></app>歷斯蕃。　皇弟分陝。每為是牧。帝室維<note n="0153065" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13592;＝翰【中研院】</note><app n="0153065"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">翰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13592;</rdg></app>。莫此之尤。劇齊<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">中</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">之</unclear>□□。□<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">河</unclear>內之擇士。遂乃褰<note n="0153066" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30907;＝襜【中研院】</note><app n="0153066"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">襜</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30907;</rdg></app>明視。戴冕來遊。繡轂朱輪。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b18"/><note n="0153067" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30908;＝聯【中研院】</note><app n="0153067"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">聯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30908;</rdg></app>清塵於往&CB00528;。鳴金繁唱。接高風之遺響。前後韋氏。大小馮君。挍德談榮。飛天伏地。屈其大道。<note n="0153068" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30909;＝烹【中研院】</note><app n="0153068"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">烹</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30909;</rdg></app>乎小鮮。張瑟調琴。裁縠製錦。賤分<note n="0153069" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30291;＝陰【中研院】</note><app n="0153069"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">陰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30291;</rdg></app>於尺璧。子<note n="0153070" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30910;＝黎【中研院】</note><app n="0153070"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">黎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30910;</rdg></app>庶而<note n="0153071" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">蒱＝蒲【中研院】</note><app n="0153071"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">蒲</lem><rdg wit="【原】">蒱</rdg></app>蘆。始布六條。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b19"/>尋能一&CB30929;。移風化俗。詎待七年。去<note n="0153072" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30911;＝煞【中研院】</note><app n="0153072"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">煞</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30911;</rdg></app><note n="0153073" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30920;＝勝【中研院】</note><app n="0153073"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">勝</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30920;</rdg></app>殘。何求百歲。政明民訟。蚩郭賀之荊州。甄屈搜賢。鄙山濤之<note n="0153074" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01005;＝冀【中研院】</note><app n="0153074"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">冀</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01005;</rdg></app>部。百城順軌。四時感德。<note n="0153075" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30291;＝陰【中研院】</note><app n="0153075"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">陰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30291;</rdg></app>陽隨意。綱目如旨。寧復二縣不雨。方待
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b20"/>車行。三郡無堪。更令徵黜。德既行焉。功亦成焉。田有遺<note n="0153076" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00295;＝糧【中研院】</note><app n="0153076"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">糧</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00295;</rdg></app>。&CB00031;無外援。蹍虺<note n="0153077" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00309;＝蛇【中研院】</note><app n="0153077"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">蛇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00309;</rdg></app>而尾<note n="0153078" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB02462;＝虎【中研院】</note><app n="0153078"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">虎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB02462;</rdg></app>豹。<note n="0153079" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30912;＝窺【中研院】</note><app n="0153079"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">窺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30912;</rdg></app>烏鵲<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">而</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">養</unclear>鳳<note n="0153080" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB05633;＝凰【中研院】</note><app n="0153080"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">凰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB05633;</rdg></app>。□車迄今。初歷七祀。自人皇出谷。分長九州。<note n="0153081" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30901;＝秉【中研院】</note><app n="0153081"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">秉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30901;</rdg></app>旄作牧。蓋無常
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b21"/>限。然梁習臨并。止餘十載。<note n="0153082" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">祌＝神【中研院】</note><app n="0153082"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">神</lem><rdg wit="【原】">祌</rdg></app>暠<note n="0153083" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30529;＝處【中研院】</note><app n="0153083"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">處</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30529;</rdg></app>益。唯乞一年。恐須<note n="0153084" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30401;＝正【中研院】</note><app n="0153084"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">正</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30401;</rdg></app>階台。載馳綸<note n="0153085" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30913;＝綍【中研院】</note><app n="0153085"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">綍</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30913;</rdg></app>。借君請帝。向天門而難<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">止</unclear>。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">臥</unclear>道興□。望雲車而無極。四民<note n="0153086" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30479;＝所【中研院】</note><app n="0153086"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30479;</rdg></app>以相告。萬里<note n="0153087" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30479;＝所【中研院】</note><app n="0153087"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30479;</rdg></app>以先憂。尋夫羊公。<note n="0153088" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30914;＝刺【中研院】</note><app n="0153088"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">刺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30914;</rdg></app>
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b22"/>□□□。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">連</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">率</unclear>梁楚。宗令周邵。親賢並播。<note n="0153089" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30477;＝椒【中研院】</note><app n="0153089"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">椒</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30477;</rdg></app>蘭俱懸。日月未<note n="0153090" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00573;＝嘗【中研院】</note><app n="0153090"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">嘗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00573;</rdg></app>矜。萬物觀一己。脆同蘆葦。空似<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">芭</unclear>蕉。縱四毒<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">之</unclear>□。任五情之馬。與夫解<note n="0153091" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30479;＝所【中研院】</note><app n="0153091"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30479;</rdg></app>未解。度<note n="0153092" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30479;＝所【中研院】</note><app n="0153092"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30479;</rdg></app>未度。安可以相論哉。我
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b23"/>王<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">夙</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">殖</unclear>善<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">根</unclear>。□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">剎</unclear>利種。以為靈光之殿。遠謝微妙之臺。<note n="0153093" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30915;＝黼【中研院】</note><app n="0153093"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">黼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30915;</rdg></app>黻之衣。誠乖精進之鎧。故以先覺而寤後覺。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">後</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">燈</unclear>而助先燈。將欲遠持三界。盡置十<note n="0153094" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB13224;＝善【中研院】</note><app n="0153094"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">善</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB13224;</rdg></app>。何直<note n="0153095" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30884;＝經【中研院】</note><app n="0153095"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">經</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30884;</rdg></app>緯文武。粉澤禮
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b24"/>樂。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">唯</unclear>然而已乎。□聞道場。攝心<note n="0153096" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00327;＝迴【中研院】</note><app n="0153096"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">迴</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00327;</rdg></app>向。隨&CB00393;供設為福田。<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">王</unclear>因以其寺名粵□□。宣尼論至道之時。乃有斯稱。軒轅念天師之教。且<note n="0153097" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">苻＝符【中研院】</note><app n="0153097"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">符</lem><rdg wit="【原】">苻</rdg></app>今旨。淨心<note n="0153098" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30479;＝所【中研院】</note><app n="0153098"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30479;</rdg></app>宅。豈與同年。兼於此伽
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b25"/>藍。更興靈塔。光光流曜。比秋月之華。蓬蓬茂出。如白雲之舉。銅槃上竦。遠承仙露。金鐸相鳴。遙驚山鬼。又<note n="0153099" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB11040;＝復【中研院】</note><app n="0153099"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB11040;</rdg></app>運藍田之玉。採荊山之珍。鏤殫變化。圖窮相好。繢渥不汙。用
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b26"/>□無染之<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">身</unclear>。夜光遍體。因現神通之色。於是竹間精舍。樹下講堂。光飾侔青鳥之蓮。珍華<note n="0153100" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30916;＝奪【中研院】</note><app n="0153100"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">奪</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30916;</rdg></app>白牛之駕。仙靈拖棟。或真聖之<note n="0153101" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB18794;＝乘【中研院】</note><app n="0153101"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">乘</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB18794;</rdg></app>煙。雲氣<note n="0153102" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30074;＝垂【中研院】</note><app n="0153102"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">垂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30074;</rdg></app><note n="0153103" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30906;＝甍【中研院】</note><app n="0153103"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">甍</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30906;</rdg></app>。<note n="0153104" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB07455;＝亂【中研院】</note><app n="0153104"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">亂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB07455;</rdg></app>峰巖之觸石。是知無生無
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b27"/>□。□有鵠林。不即不離。茲亦鷲嶺。道本一准。勿輕像法之期。佛乃旡<note n="0153105" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30565;＝邊【中研院】</note><app n="0153105"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">邊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30565;</rdg></app>。何偏王舍之界。寺去州城餘二百里。扶<note n="0153106" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB08668;＝桑【中研院】</note><app n="0153106"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">桑</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08668;</rdg></app>初曉。楊枝始嚼。塵消氣滅。霧卷霞除。昇高峰。<note n="0153107" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30917;＝望【中研院】</note><app n="0153107"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">望</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30917;</rdg></app>都邑。朱
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b28"/><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">樓</unclear>紫閣。真雲中之化欲來。綠樹丹城。像域外之飛將至。分明可見。異隴首之望平川。&CB00565;散高情。踰岱宗之小天下。壯哉峻極。麗矣莊嚴。何但名相佛土。頗<note n="0153108" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30910;＝黎【中研院】</note><app n="0153108"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">黎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30910;</rdg></app>為地。法<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">明</unclear>出
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b29"/>世。天宮近人。齊聖廣淵也如彼。菩提道<note n="0153109" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30918;＝身【中研院】</note><app n="0153109"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">身</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30918;</rdg></app>也如此。自可生蓮花於<note n="0153110" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30919;＝鬲【中研院】</note><app n="0153110"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">鬲</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30919;</rdg></app>子。樊烈火於魔宮。屏息而獲法雲。翹足而俟授記。寧<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">止</unclear>延　皇家卜年之數。增我　后　王佐之功。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b30"/>井藤相促。城芥將滿。庶願力護持。群神肅翼。須<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">彌</unclear>腐敗。<note n="0153111" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30920;＝勝【中研院】</note><app n="0153111"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">勝</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30920;</rdg></app>地莫渝。玄圃飛浮。神山琠T。今歲在<note n="0153112" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30404;＝赤【中研院】</note><app n="0153112"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">赤</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30404;</rdg></app><note n="0153113" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30921;＝奮【中研院】</note><app n="0153113"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">奮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30921;</rdg></app>。時惟青秖。陽殖官杏。日望月桂。<note n="0153114" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30922;＝斲【中研院】</note><app n="0153114"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">斲</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30922;</rdg></app>磨瑊&CB06499;。明揚<note n="0153115" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00655;＝鼓【中研院】</note><app n="0153115"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">鼓</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00655;</rdg></app>鍾。縱漢帝種桃。屢
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b31"/>獲花&CB00031;。麻姑看海。數移陵陸。猶望有類粟山。記戊申之歲。更同荊峴。見望拜之碑。無愧之詞。乃為銘曰。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b32"/>即林嘉遁。歸山長<note n="0153116" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30927;＝住【中研院】</note><app n="0153116"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">住</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30927;</rdg></app>。未極人天。猶居塵壤。我有福地。<note n="0153117" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30928;＝全【中研院】</note><app n="0153117"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">全</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30928;</rdg></app>疑安養。閣&CB00153;珠羅。樓懸金<note n="0153118" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB08051;＝網【中研院】</note><app n="0153118"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">網</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB08051;</rdg></app>。峰高萬刃。<note n="0153119" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00117;＝澗【中研院】</note><app n="0153119"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">澗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00117;</rdg></app>遠千尋。煙雲出入。仙聖登臨。谷幽虛囀。松高自吟。紫芝咸迾。丹桂成□。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b33"/>彼有人焉。創茲虛境。高<note n="0153120" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00275;＝窗【中研院】</note><app n="0153120"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">窗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00275;</rdg></app>蔭柏。危櫚承嶺。野曠村稀。巖空人靜。草呼風氣。池搖月影。嘿形端拱。凝神丘壑。搖錫褰衣。遨遊林薄。思滅毒火。求分良藥。遠棄形骸。蕭然寥□。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b34"/>曆窮於坎。倉精受命。陵躪百王。懸衡七政。洛<note n="0153121" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">苻＝符【中研院】</note><app n="0153121"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">符</lem><rdg wit="【原】">苻</rdg></app><note n="0153122" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00283;＝效【中研院】</note><app n="0153122"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">效</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00283;</rdg></app>祉。河文標聖。朝眾水神。國多天鏡。本枝磐石。如珪如璧。龍變成章。鵬飛舉翮。閤延髦士。庭多捐客。高義盈門。清談滿席。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b35"/>燕南趙北。奇士爰臻。盧河通氣。白壤飄塵。<note n="0153123" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30291;＝陰【中研院】</note><app n="0153123"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">陰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30291;</rdg></app>陽<note n="0153124" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30479;＝所【中研院】</note><app n="0153124"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30479;</rdg></app>合。風雨攸均。輕軒高蓋。來慰斯民。卬泥作豉。牧羊調馬。德通靈物。謠成風雅。寬猛春秋。愛畏冬夏。并州陵段。<note n="0153125" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB01005;＝冀【中研院】</note><app n="0153125"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">冀</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB01005;</rdg></app>方踰□。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b36"/>爰觀六趣。尚想三塗。香珍<note n="0153126" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30923;＝薝【中研院】</note><app n="0153126"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">薝</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30923;</rdg></app>匐。道慕拘盧。化城度嶮。抨酪求蘇。既雕宮觀。有類蓬<note n="0153127" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30924;＝壺【中研院】</note><app n="0153127"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">壺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30924;</rdg></app>。百雉攸遠。九成<note n="0153128" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30924;＝迢【中研院】</note><app n="0153128"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">迢</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30924;</rdg></app><note n="0153129" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30925;＝遰【中研院】</note><app n="0153129"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">遰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30925;</rdg></app>。薄霧輕籠。微煙少<note n="0153130" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00877;＝蔽【中研院】</note><app n="0153130"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">蔽</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00877;</rdg></app>。光風新靜。暾暉初麗。極目相望。地<note n="0153131" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB18794;＝乘【中研院】</note><app n="0153131"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">乘</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB18794;</rdg></app>天際。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b37"/><note n="0153132" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30897;＝斗【中研院】</note><app n="0153132"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">斗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30897;</rdg></app><note n="0153133" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00327;＝迴【中研院】</note><app n="0153133"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">迴</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00327;</rdg></app>南北。日轉西東。遑遑馳驟。抵速<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">人</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">中</unclear>。地煎熱水。天壞<note n="0153134" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00321;＝災【中研院】</note><app n="0153134"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">災</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00321;</rdg></app>風。願將此<note n="0153135" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30529;＝處【中研院】</note><app n="0153135"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【中研院】">處</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30529;</rdg></app>。懸置虛空。
                            <lb ed="I" n="0153b38"/>　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　大齊天保八年歲在丁丑<unclear cert="high" reason="damage">二</unclear><unclear cert="high" reason="damage">月</unclear>戊辰十五日壬午刊記
